Dashboard

Welcome to the Intelligent Traffic Anomaly Detection System Dashboard.

Features

  • Accept uploaded traffic videos or live streams.
  • Detect vehicles, persons, helmets, and emergency vehicles.
  • Detect footpath violations.
  • Detect wrong-way driving.
  • Detect entry into prohibited zones.
  • Detect over-speeding violations.
  • Track object trajectories.
  • Detect accidents using two approaches.
  • Identify emergency vehicles and apply rule exemptions.

Dashboard Functionality

This dashboard will provide real-time monitoring, analytics, and management tools for traffic anomaly detection.

Further development will integrate live video streams, detection results, and user controls.

); } export default Dashboard;
